2015-11-18   Jamie Tattersall <tattersall@physik.rwth-aachen.de>

    ~ Bugfix in AnalysisManager when total error is not provided by user  (thanks to Liangliang Shang)

2015-11-02   Jamie Tattersall <tattersall@physik.rwth-aachen.de>

    ~ Various bugfixes for atlas_1407_0583 (thanks to Liangliang Shang)

